{"tid":1827270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中華民國台灣」是蔡英文分裂國民黨的手段","createTime":"2020-01-16T23:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T06:52:16.000Z","uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a79a665d1cf601c7e37005d88d08d09fb4b3150","tid":1827270,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:40:25.000Z","msg":"國民黨老中青三代都很清楚，台獨是民進黨神主牌，中華民國四字就是國民黨碩果僅存的招牌。<br />\n<br />\n當民進黨也開始喊中華民國，而且反共愛國做得比國民黨還好，那等於是奪走國民黨賴以集結眾人的信仰。<br />\n<br />\n把這看成是裂解國民黨的暫時過程，比起國民被其他類似性質的政黨，如親民黨、民眾黨取代，更有實質意義。<br />\n<br />\n通過《反滲透法》的民進黨才是檯面上最守護中華民國的政黨，愛國青年們早該放棄國民黨；那些在議會要求蔡英文宣佈獨立的聲音也變得不痛不癢，因為民進黨早就沒有獨不獨立的問題，他們就是獨立國家"},{"pid":"0ffe2195930c3872e62f6a6298e1d9344a78c2b9","tid":1827270,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c05646b2eb59742799d69e5ef1708ca9066e4","tid":1827270,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦 你喜啦"},{"pid":"452d8f8173f89791cd6728c8e237f16b4d3eee68","tid":1827270,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2b41919deeac008044918ab72cb2522ccb33e7","tid":1827270,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cc2cb5fc354a17c7d1ec87b7910236c67ba9ed","tid":1827270,"uid":263261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又露底啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都扮左好耐"},{"pid":"178202488f09daa0